## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a582a-102">当对象引发<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs> 事件<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted>时, 将创建的实例。 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a582a-102">An instance of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs> is created when the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> object raises the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted> event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a582a-103">若要获取有关识别结果的信息, 请访问<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A>事件处理程序中的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a582a-103">To obtain information about the result of recognition, access the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> property in the handler for the event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a582a-104">模拟是指文本而不是音频, 是语音识别引擎的输入。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a582a-104">Emulation is the process by which text, instead of audio, is the input to a speech recognition engine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a582a-105">若要在仿真期间绕过<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>对象的音频输入, 请<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SetInputToNull%2A>使用方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a582a-105">To bypass the audio inputs for a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> object during emulation, use the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SetInputToNull%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a582a-106">如果语音识别引擎在识别操作期间遇到异常, 则<xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>属性将设置为异常, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A>并将属性设置为`null`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a582a-106">If the speech recognition engine encounters an exception during the recognition operation, the <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A> property is set to the exception and the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> property is set to `null`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a582a-107"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs> 派生自 <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a582a-107"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs> derives from <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a582a-108">下面的示例将<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted>事件的事件处理程序添加<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a582a-108">The following example adds an event handler for the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted> event to a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a582a-109">处理程序从<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A>属性获取识别的文本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a582a-109">The handler gets the recognized text from the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
private SpeechRecognitionEngine sre;  
  
// Initialize the speech recognition engine.   
private void Initialize()  
{  
  sre = new SpeechRecognitionEngine();  
  
  // Add a handler for the EmulateRecognizeCompleted event.  
  sre.EmulateRecognizeCompleted += new EventHandler<EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs>(sre_EmulateRecognizeCompleted);  
  
  // Add other initialization code here.  
}  
  
// Handle the EmulateRecognizeCompleted event.   
void sre_EmulateRecognizeCompleted(object sender, EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs e)  
{  
  if (e.Result == null) return;  
  
  string phrase = e.Result.Text;  
  
  // Add event handler code here.  
}  
  
```
